snippet.title: Diana and Roma in the Escape Room Challenge
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma enter the escape room. Children need to find 7 keys to open the lock and get out. An interesting adventure in the quest room with activities for children - training the mind, dexterity and quick wits.
Thanks for watching!
